the long-term client that Zhang Yan
has been keeping in touch with,

575
00:23:35,730 --> 00:23:36,900
Ms. Li Bingmei,

576
00:23:36,950 --> 00:23:39,470
added 10,000 yuan to her account here

577
00:23:40,100 --> 00:23:42,990
to purchase our products and services.

578
00:23:42,990 --> 00:23:45,230
That's genuine care
winning genuine trust.

579
00:23:45,230 --> 00:23:47,340
Let's give Zhang Yan
a round of applause.

580
00:24:03,670 --> 00:24:05,500
Have a taste of this wine.

581
00:24:05,740 --> 00:24:07,110
It's different from the last one.

582
00:24:12,710 --> 00:24:13,550
How is it?

583
00:24:14,670 --> 00:24:15,510
Pretty good.

584
00:24:16,430 --> 00:24:17,340
Thanks, Mr. Ma.

585
00:24:17,580 --> 00:24:19,100
I appreciate all your help lately.

586
00:24:19,340 --> 00:24:21,150
I should be the one
treating you to dinner.

587
00:24:21,950 --> 00:24:23,150
You treating me?

588
00:24:23,540 --> 00:24:24,390
I'm your boss.

589
00:24:24,390 --> 00:24:25,580
Do you think I need that?

590
00:24:26,500 --> 00:24:27,950
You earn your money the hard way.

591
00:24:27,950 --> 00:24:28,910
Keep it for yourself.

592
00:24:31,740 --> 00:24:33,950
From your accent,
you're not local to Pingtan, are you?

593
00:24:34,470 --> 00:24:35,340
No.

594
00:24:35,430 --> 00:24:37,150
I'm from Shimen.

595
00:24:38,340 --> 00:24:39,630
Do you have any siblings?

596
00:24:39,630 --> 00:24:41,300
Yeah, I've got a younger brother.

597
00:24:41,470 --> 00:24:43,100
He's still in school.

598
00:24:46,150 --> 00:24:47,670
Is Mengmeng going to be okay

599
00:24:47,670 --> 00:24:48,870
when we're having dinner?

600
00:24:48,870 --> 00:24:49,710
It's fine.

601
00:24:49,710 --> 00:24:50,740
I've asked a neighbor

602
00:24:50,740 --> 00:24:52,340
to take care of her.

603
00:24:55,950 --> 00:24:57,110
It must've been hard for you.

604
00:24:58,340 --> 00:24:59,390
When I look at you,

605
00:24:59,390 --> 00:25:01,200
it feels like I'm looking
at my younger self

606
00:25:01,230 --> 00:25:03,230
when I first came to Pingtan
to make a living.

607
00:25:03,740 --> 00:25:05,580
I didn't know anyone or anything.

608
00:25:05,950 --> 00:25:07,430
Whatever kind of trouble I ran into,

609
00:25:07,430 --> 00:25:08,910
I had to push through it on my own.

610
00:25:09,500 --> 00:25:10,920
But things are even tougher for you.

611
00:25:11,430 --> 00:25:12,670
You've got a kid.

612
00:25:15,950 --> 00:25:17,150
Where's your husband?

613
00:25:19,100 --> 00:25:19,950
He passed away.

614
00:25:25,430 --> 00:25:26,270
Sorry to hear that.

615
00:25:26,670 --> 00:25:27,820
It's okay.

616
00:25:30,670 --> 00:25:31,670
Alright, let's drop it.

617
00:25:31,670 --> 00:25:32,670
Come on, have a drink.

618
00:25:35,580 --> 00:25:36,420
Bottom-up.

619
00:26:03,990 --> 00:26:04,830
What's wrong?

620
00:26:05,580 --> 00:26:06,420
Do you want to stop?

621
00:26:08,070 --> 00:26:08,910
No.

622
00:26:08,910 --> 00:26:09,910
I can drink.

623
00:26:12,630 --> 00:26:14,910
If you don't want to, just say so.

624
00:26:15,740 --> 00:26:16,670
It's okay.

625
00:26:17,820 --> 00:26:19,500
Like when work gets tough,

626
00:26:19,500 --> 00:26:20,500
you should speak up.

627
00:26:22,870 --> 00:26:24,390
You gotta be honest with yourself.

628
00:26:25,820 --> 00:26:27,300
I don't like this side of you.

629
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:28,390
Mr. Ma.

630
00:26:28,390 --> 00:26:31,670
A person should first look inward

631
00:26:32,430 --> 00:26:34,230
and then learn
to feel the world outside.

632
00:26:35,670 --> 00:26:36,510
Got it?

633
00:26:38,430 --> 00:26:40,150
It's not about you, Mr. Ma.

634
00:26:40,150 --> 00:26:41,470
I just can't hold my liquor.

635
00:26:41,670 --> 00:26:42,510
I...

636
00:26:44,470 --> 00:26:45,580
Alright, come on.

637
00:26:45,580 --> 00:26:46,500
Stop drinking then.

638
00:26:49,150 --> 00:26:50,670
When I saw you for the first time,

639
00:26:51,340 --> 00:26:53,100
you were out in the rain
handing out flyers.

640
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:54,740
No one else would go.

641
00:26:54,850 --> 00:26:55,900
Why were you the only one?

642
00:26:55,940 --> 00:26:57,090
Did you want to put on a show

643
00:26:57,090 --> 00:26:58,050
to earn people's praise?

644
00:26:58,070 --> 00:26:58,980
No.

645
00:26:59,990 --> 00:27:01,870
I just noticed no one else wanted to go.

646
00:27:01,870 --> 00:27:02,910
I didn't mind.

647
00:27:02,910 --> 00:27:03,650
You didn't mind?

648
00:27:03,660 --> 00:27:04,910
Why would you be the only one?

649
00:27:04,910 --> 00:27:05,750
I...

650
00:27:05,950 --> 00:27:07,670
I've never minded anything.

651
00:27:07,670 --> 00:27:08,740
What?

652
00:27:08,740 --> 00:27:09,990
Nonsense. You're lying.

653
00:27:09,990 --> 00:27:11,340
Seriously, Mr. Ma.

654
00:27:11,950 --> 00:27:13,430
I just don't mind.

655
00:27:15,820 --> 00:27:16,740
When I was a kid,

656
00:27:16,740 --> 00:27:19,060
my brother and I both wanted ice cream,

657
00:27:19,470 --> 00:27:20,870
but my family didn't buy one for me,

658
00:27:20,870 --> 00:27:23,470
and I didn't mind, either.

659
00:27:23,870 --> 00:27:24,710
Later,

660
00:27:24,910 --> 00:27:27,150
I only met Mengmeng's dad once,

661
00:27:27,150 --> 00:27:28,670
and they suggested we get married.

662
00:27:29,150 --> 00:27:30,910
I didn't mind, either.

663
00:27:31,910 --> 00:27:34,150
None of them ever asked me.

664
00:27:38,150 --> 00:27:40,100
I didn't mean you had to ask me.

665
00:27:40,470 --> 00:27:41,340
I...

666
00:27:41,340 --> 00:27:42,430
I don't know how to say it.

667
00:27:42,430 --> 00:27:43,740
Honestly, I don't mind.

668
00:27:45,150 --> 00:27:47,340
I shouldn't be telling you this.

669
00:27:48,740 --> 00:27:50,910
When Mengmeng's dad didn't come back

670
00:27:52,740 --> 00:27:53,950
from fishing,

671
00:27:54,470 --> 00:27:56,470
everyone told me he was dead.

672
00:27:57,430 --> 00:27:58,870
I didn't ask about it, either.

673
00:27:59,430 --> 00:28:01,150
I didn't mind.

674
00:28:01,670 --> 00:28:02,870
You didn't mind?

675
00:28:09,100 --> 00:28:10,300
Zhang Yan, listen.

676
00:28:12,060 --> 00:28:13,190
Sometimes,

677
00:28:14,430 --> 00:28:17,500
you're tougher than you think.

678
00:28:22,300 --> 00:28:24,230
But I don't need
that toughness from you.

679
00:28:26,470 --> 00:28:28,340
I just want to see the real you.

680
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:33,630
The real me?

681
00:28:34,910 --> 00:28:37,390
The real me has nothing at all.

682
00:28:40,100 --> 00:28:40,940
Come on.

683
00:28:55,710 --> 00:28:57,150
Do you know what matters most?

684
00:29:00,340 --> 00:29:02,670
It's not about how many people like you

685
00:29:02,670 --> 00:29:04,150
or how many love you;

686
00:29:05,430 --> 00:29:06,340
it is

687
00:29:06,910 --> 00:29:08,500
about whether you're worth being loved.

688
00:29:12,470 --> 00:29:13,340
Look at me.

689
00:29:15,430 --> 00:29:16,950
The woman in my eyes now

690
00:29:18,390 --> 00:29:19,710
is the real you.

691
00:29:21,870 --> 00:29:23,670
She deserves to be treated with care.

692
00:30:39,910 --> 00:30:40,760
Mr. Ma.

693
00:30:40,770 --> 00:30:41,660
You're awake.

694
00:30:41,670 --> 00:30:42,630
Have some breakfast.

695
00:30:44,500 --> 00:30:45,390
I...

696
00:30:46,150 --> 00:30:47,430
You were drunk last night.

697
00:30:47,740 --> 00:30:48,990
I helped you back to my room.

698
00:30:49,150 --> 00:30:50,190
I slept in the guest room.

699
00:30:51,950 --> 00:30:53,630
Oh, your phone's charged.

700
00:30:54,950 --> 00:30:55,790
Okay.

701
00:30:59,790 --> 00:31:01,990
Your neighbor
kept calling you last night.

702
00:31:01,990 --> 00:31:03,100
I answer it for you.

703
00:31:03,790 --> 00:31:06,390
She said Mengmeng was home alone
with no one to look after her,

704
00:31:06,470 --> 00:31:08,100
so I asked her to help.

705
00:31:08,430 --> 00:31:09,710
Remember to thank her today.

706
00:31:11,300 --> 00:31:12,190
Thank you, Mr. Ma.

707
00:31:15,340 --> 00:31:16,590
If you really want to thank me,

708
00:31:16,870 --> 00:31:18,710
stop calling me Mr. Ma
when we're off work.

709
00:31:22,950 --> 00:31:23,790
Also,

710
00:31:25,150 --> 00:31:26,300
what I said yesterday

711
00:31:26,950 --> 00:31:28,170
wasn't just the drink talking.

712
00:31:40,950 --> 00:31:43,340
What made you suddenly want
to go shopping with me today?

713
00:31:44,430 --> 00:31:45,430
Are you in love?

714
00:31:47,390 --> 00:31:48,230
No.

715
00:31:49,670 --> 00:31:50,950
I just got paid and wanted

716
00:31:50,950 --> 00:31:52,430
to buy myself something new.

717
00:31:55,150 --> 00:31:56,060
This one looks good.

718
00:32:00,910 --> 00:32:02,100
It really suits you.

719
00:32:46,430 --> 00:32:47,820
You look a bit different today.

720
00:32:55,470 --> 00:32:56,910
Do you think this looks good on me?

721
00:34:40,870 --> 00:34:41,950
I've told you.

722
00:34:44,430 --> 00:34:45,910
What I love is the real you.

723
00:35:29,100 --> 00:35:31,100
What I love is the real you.

724
00:35:39,620 --> 00:35:42,460
(Win with Influence;
Become a Millionaire in Seven Years)

725
00:36:05,020 --> 00:36:05,910
Did you sleep well?

726
00:36:10,390 --> 00:36:11,750
Move in with me.

727
00:36:12,540 --> 00:36:14,310
When Ma Weicheng treated me well,

728
00:36:14,950 --> 00:36:15,990
he could be really nice.

729
00:36:16,540 --> 00:36:17,430
Bring Mengmeng, too.

730
00:36:17,430 --> 00:36:18,950
Though he'd done a lot of things

731
00:36:18,950 --> 00:36:20,180
that really scared me...

732
00:36:21,220 --> 00:36:22,350
Let me take care of you.

733
00:36:23,540 --> 00:36:25,100
... He also said he loved me.

734
00:36:25,790 --> 00:36:27,010
He said I deserve to be loved.

735
00:36:30,500 --> 00:36:31,820
Maybe because, since I was little,

736
00:36:31,820 --> 00:36:33,470
I've never been loved properly,

737
00:36:34,950 --> 00:36:36,750
I honestly mistook that for love.

738
00:36:40,430 --> 00:36:41,270
But that wasn't love.

739
00:36:42,500 --> 00:36:43,830
That was just hurting you.

740
00:36:46,830 --> 00:36:48,100
He said you deserved love?

741
00:36:49,430 --> 00:36:50,280
If he thought that,

742
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:51,870
why control what you wear?

743
00:36:52,910 --> 00:36:54,350
How is that supposed to be love?

744
00:36:55,470 --> 00:36:57,350
He was just testing
how far he could push you

745
00:36:57,350 --> 00:36:58,890
and trying to control you step by step.

746
00:36:59,870 --> 00:37:00,710
Yeah.

747
00:37:01,540 --> 00:37:02,700
Looking back now,

748
00:37:03,390 --> 00:37:05,350
I realize
that when he was nice to me at first,

749
00:37:05,410 --> 00:37:07,290
it was to figure out
what kind of woman I was.

750
00:37:07,580 --> 00:37:08,990
He wanted to find my weak spots,

751
00:37:10,220 --> 00:37:12,270
so he could use them against me.

752
00:37:14,390 --> 00:37:16,020
Once he saw my insecurities,

753
00:37:17,790 --> 00:37:19,390
I became easy for him to control.

754
00:37:20,430 --> 00:37:21,540
Like a trap.

755
00:37:22,870 --> 00:37:24,700
He drew an invisible circle around you,

756
00:37:25,910 --> 00:37:27,160
and that circle kept shrinking

757
00:37:27,500 --> 00:37:28,870
bit by bit

758
00:37:31,430 --> 00:37:33,430
until there was only you and him inside.

759
00:37:34,060 --> 00:37:35,800
Then your whole world
revolved around him.

760
00:37:37,220 --> 00:37:38,180
You're right.

761
00:37:41,180 --> 00:37:43,270
Everyone got paid this afternoon,

762
00:37:44,470 --> 00:37:45,750
except for me.

763
00:37:46,470 --> 00:37:47,350
I did that on purpose.

764
00:37:52,220 --> 00:37:53,100
Just messing with you.

765
00:37:54,060 --> 00:37:56,750
I bought an education fund for Mengmeng.

766
00:37:57,310 --> 00:37:59,390
It's only a few thousand each month.

767
00:37:59,990 --> 00:38:01,910
So, when she goes to college,

768
00:38:01,910 --> 00:38:02,910
we won't have to worry.

769
00:38:09,220 --> 00:38:10,060
Look.

770
00:38:13,750 --> 00:38:14,620
That's quite a bit.

771
00:38:17,700 --> 00:38:18,950
It's really good.

772
00:38:19,620 --> 00:38:21,430
But my salary might not cover it.

773
00:38:22,540 --> 00:38:23,890
You've got me to help, don't you?

774
00:38:25,220 --> 00:38:26,310
Now that we're together,

775
00:38:26,580 --> 00:38:28,360
there's no need
to separate yours and mine.

776
00:38:29,540 --> 00:38:30,620
I'll put all our money

777
00:38:31,020 --> 00:38:32,020
into one bank card.

778
00:38:32,750 --> 00:38:34,540
Whenever you need it, just tell me.

779
00:38:37,910 --> 00:38:39,310
Let's be more careful with spending,

780
00:38:39,310 --> 00:38:40,430
and it'll be fine.

781
00:38:41,430 --> 00:38:42,490
We should think long-term

782
00:38:42,950 --> 00:38:43,990
for Mengmeng

783
00:38:45,390 --> 00:38:46,830
and our future.

784
00:39:00,250 --> 00:39:01,100
Thanks.

785
00:39:01,100 --> 00:39:01,940
Thank you.

786
00:39:03,500 --> 00:39:04,390
Ms. Xu,

787
00:39:04,790 --> 00:39:06,430
I'll pass on the drink.

788
00:39:06,430 --> 00:39:06,980
Have one.

789
00:39:06,980 --> 00:39:08,430
It's not easy for us to get together.

790
00:39:08,430 --> 00:39:09,620
Take it.

791
00:39:09,830 --> 00:39:10,750
Yeah, come on.

792
00:39:13,350 --> 00:39:14,430
Come on, let's drink.

793
00:39:14,430 --> 00:39:15,270
Cheers!

794
00:39:20,990 --> 00:39:21,830
Oh, Zhang Yan.

795
00:39:22,270 --> 00:39:23,110
My husband's cousin

796
00:39:23,110 --> 00:39:24,740
came to Pingtan to visit us
a while back.

797
00:39:24,910 --> 00:39:26,790
After he left,
he started asking me about you.

798
00:39:26,790 --> 00:39:28,220
Do you have someone you like?

799
00:39:28,220 --> 00:39:30,870
She's definitely seeing someone.

800
00:39:30,870 --> 00:39:31,910
No, I'm not.

801
00:39:31,910 --> 00:39:34,310
Your smile gives it away every day.

802
00:39:34,310 --> 00:39:36,950
We even went shopping days ago.

803
00:39:38,270 --> 00:39:39,790
Why aren't you wearing that dress?

804
00:39:40,310 --> 00:39:41,790
Who were you planning to show it to?

805
00:39:41,790 --> 00:39:42,870
No one.

806
00:39:43,540 --> 00:39:44,580
I just haven't put it on.

807
00:40:05,020 --> 00:40:06,060
I'm back.

808
00:40:12,870 --> 00:40:14,090
Did you buy the ink cartridge?

809
00:40:15,620 --> 00:40:16,620
I forgot.

810
00:40:17,430 --> 00:40:19,430
Do you need it right now?
I can go get one.

811
00:40:19,430 --> 00:40:20,310
Did you drink?

812
00:40:23,220 --> 00:40:24,470
Everyone was having fun,

813
00:40:24,830 --> 00:40:26,270
so I had a little.

814
00:40:32,620 --> 00:40:33,950
Do you think

815
00:40:34,700 --> 00:40:36,110
what I say doesn't matter anymore?

816
00:40:39,690 --> 00:40:40,870
Do you even care about me now?

817
00:40:40,870 --> 00:40:41,750
Of course, I do.

818
00:40:43,470 --> 00:40:44,870
Then how could you forget?

819
00:40:46,060 --> 00:40:46,900
I'll go right now...

820
00:41:01,310 --> 00:41:02,150
Mengmeng.

821
00:41:02,830 --> 00:41:03,870
I'm here.

822
00:41:06,870 --> 00:41:07,750
It's okay.

823
00:41:07,750 --> 00:41:08,700
It's fine.

824
00:41:10,020 --> 00:41:11,270
It's okay, Mengmeng.

825
00:41:11,540 --> 00:41:12,430
I'm right here.

826
00:41:13,620 --> 00:41:14,460
It's alright.

827
00:41:37,270 --> 00:41:37,830
Do you think

828
00:41:37,830 --> 00:41:39,310
I'm being selfish by not letting you

829
00:41:39,310 --> 00:41:40,430
tell them about us?

830
00:41:41,350 --> 00:41:42,190
No, not at all.

831
00:41:43,430 --> 00:41:44,910
I know you were looking out for me.

832
00:41:45,910 --> 00:41:46,750
Zhang Yan,

833
00:41:47,470 --> 00:41:48,430
in this world,

834
00:41:48,790 --> 00:41:50,870
not everyone is as kind as you imagine.

835
00:41:52,220 --> 00:41:53,470
If they find out about us,

836
00:41:53,870 --> 00:41:55,430
they'll talk behind your back at work.

837
00:41:56,390 --> 00:41:57,750
That'd be bad for you.

838
00:41:57,750 --> 00:41:58,910
I just wanted to protect you.

839
00:42:04,430 --> 00:42:05,350
I know.

840
00:42:18,430 --> 00:42:19,270
I'm sorry.

841
00:42:21,270 --> 00:42:22,790
I lost my temper just now.

842
00:42:23,310 --> 00:42:24,750
I shouldn't have gotten that angry.

843
00:42:26,750 --> 00:42:27,590
Please forgive me.

844
00:42:28,060 --> 00:42:28,900
Okay?

845
00:43:08,430 --> 00:43:10,500
Don't hang out
with those people anymore.

846
00:43:11,950 --> 00:43:13,310
You've got me and Mengmeng.

847
00:43:13,790 --> 00:43:14,830
That's all you need.

848
00:43:19,340 --> 00:43:23,860
(Longxiang Travel & Transport Co., Ltd.)

849
00:43:28,870 --> 00:43:29,790
I haven't gone out

850
00:43:29,800 --> 00:43:32,100
for fun in years.

851
00:43:32,870 --> 00:43:34,830
That's sweet of you to plan this.

852
00:43:37,870 --> 00:43:38,790
Zhang,

853
00:43:39,020 --> 00:43:40,180
I often think

854
00:43:40,580 --> 00:43:42,870
that if I had a daughter like you,

855
00:43:42,870 --> 00:43:43,950
that would be wonderful.

856
